just_use dsl_planner.py

# label: EARLY
# role: generate a DSL program that cleans a dirty board

The OLDER planner system (peel/park/extend/dissolve/home
verb vocabulary; see `dsl_player.py`'s docstring). Pre-dates
`bfs_solver.py`. Currently used by `test_dsl_planner.py`
(known FAIL "planner stuck" — pre-existing).

Pairs with `board_classifier.py` (the typed-board view) and
`dsl_player.py` (parse + execute).

## Status

Not load-bearing for the corpus baseline today. Kept around
because `bfs_solver`'s success doesn't fully retire the
prior vocabulary, and Steve hasn't yet decided whether the
older pipeline retires or stays as a separate channel.

## TODO

- Decide: retire the entire DSL pipeline
  (`dsl.py`, `dsl_planner.py`, `dsl_player.py`,
